Create the below directories if they does not exist already
- mkdir /usr/local/hyperv
- mkdir /var/opt/hyperv

Copy all the Script files and source files to /usr/local/hyperv 
- cp -R * /usr/local/hyperv/
Check /usr/local/hyperv folder for files

How to compile the daemon code 
- gcc -o hv_kvp_daemon hv_kvp_daemon.c

Set the exectuing permissions for script and executable using chmod command
- chmod 755 hv_get_dns_info hv_get_dhcp_info hv_set_ifconfig hv_kvp_daemon

Copy hv_kvpd script to /etc/rc.d/
- cp hv_kvpd /etc/rc.d/
Set exectuing permissions using chmod command 
- chmod 755 hv_kvpd

- Edit rc.conf file - Add 
hv_kvp_daemon_enable="YES"

Reboot the machine - it will start hv_kvp_daemon and load hv_utils.ko driver.
- reboot
